#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.diagonal:56
msgid ""
"If `a` is 2-D, then a 1-D array containing the diagonal and of the same type "
"as `a` is returned unless `a` is a `matrix`, in which case a 1-D array "
"rather than a (2-D) `matrix` is returned in order to maintain backward "
"compatibility."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.diagonal:61
msgid ""
"If ``a.ndim > 2``, then the dimensions specified by `axis1` and `axis2` are "
"removed, and a new axis inserted at the end corresponding to the diagonal."
msgstr ""

